#inline#mFMb_DS_GetIdleCounter( idleMode )/*	What it does:	It gets the number of times the given idle mode has been looped through by the plug-in since FileMaker startup.		Required parameters:		idleMode	"safeIlde", "semiSafeIdle" of "unSafeIdle"		notes:	For more information, see the example file "Idle Modes".		returns:	the number of idle loops			could return myFMbutler error 9 / Evaluation error 1224*/